"title": "4236: fountain",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4236",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A source of natural spring water. Figuratively, it symbolises a place of cleansing, tears or sexual fulfilment. Significantly, God is pictured as a fountain of life.</p>\n<h2>The fountain as a source of spring water</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:4\">PRO 18:4</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of fountains</h2>\n<h3>A place of cleansing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:1\">ZEC 13:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Tears of inconsolable grief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:1\">JER 9:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Sexual fulfilment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:12\">SNG 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:15-Prov5:18\">PRO 5:15–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:15\">SNG 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>A source of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:27\">PRO 14:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:8-Ps36:9\">PSA 36:8–36:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps87:7\">PSA 87:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:11\">PRO 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:14\">PRO 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:22\">PRO 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:18\">JOL 3:18</a></p>",
